{"tid":714010,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"小學雞數理挑戰 (不定期更新)","createTime":"2018-06-23T10:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T02:30:46.000Z","uid":187216,"like":5,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"76c497f734dcf13cb0289a27f268111fd753b71a","tid":714010,"uid":187216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"呢排見啲小學雞問嘢俾人屌，屌完又好似冇咩得著咁，所以响網上搵咗啲問題考考啲小學雞：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/180101_a70ebd0341cb6b801b0c26cd4ab7b00b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F180101_a70ebd0341cb6b801b0c26cd4ab7b00b.png&h=a4148217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗱，2^33 = 8,589,934,592，即佢個位數係2。<br />\n3^33 = 5,559,060,566,555,523，即佢個位數係3。<br />\n<br />\n咁加哂89個33次方，嗰個位數係咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n數學撚技癢就玩下面呢條：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/180859_a9c0b02d93f177e874523e898fd16714.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F180859_a9c0b02d93f177e874523e898fd16714.png&h=143d6b48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebfe3f2bc7ba853d2f160d0efb4903f7cdb421b8","tid":714010,"uid":33643,"like":14,"dislike":6,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收皮啦大陸狗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/165317_3c5d525ac55b7521b6d20238c67749c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F165317_3c5d525ac55b7521b6d20238c67749c4.png&h=38f91759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/165317_19cc0bd5da61ae899669ade3ddb5e351.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F165317_19cc0bd5da61ae899669ade3ddb5e351.png&h=0